<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.1">
<l>ciṅkamatā yavuṇaṉ tiṟalākamuṉ kīṇṭukanta</l>
<l>caṅkamiṭat tāṉait taḻalāḻiva lattāṉai</l>
<l>ceṅkamalat tayaṉaṉaiyār teṉṉaḻuntai yilmaṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṅkamalak kaṇṇaṉai yaṭiyēṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, [his] servant, saw for myself the one at whose left is the conch,</l>
<l>The one at whose right is the fiery disc, the one with lovely lotus eyes</l>
<l>Who, becoming a lion, was satisfied long ago having split</l>
<l rend="indent">the demon’s stalwart chest,</l>
<l>Who eternally stands in Aḻuntai of the south</l>
<l rend="indent">with those like unborn [Brahmā] on the red lotus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
